snippet.title: Brother Bear - Game Boy Advance Longplay [HD]
snippet.description:
Name: Disney's Brother Bear

Description: Disney's Brother Bear immerses you in a fully interactive version of Kenai's world, complete with the lush environments based on the animated film. Join Kenai and Koda as they make their way through various areas in the forest.

Release Date: November 2003

Played on: Game Boy Advance (mGBA) 

Subscribe: http://www.youtube.com/channel/UCKyqN3jWJgSfAuxCBt5zn3A?sub_confirmation=1
